The paper discusses the SP theory of intelligence and its potential applications in various fields such as unsupervised learning, pattern recognition, and probabilistic reasoning. These topics are closely related to the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
